  "description": [
    "2 WERE WINNING IN VIETNAM US Picked Right Ally To Stand Against Reds Editors Note Richard Tregaskis is the author of the classic eyewitness reports of fighting men in action Guadacanal Diary Invasion Diary Mission Over Korea Last Plane To Shanghai Force Os Arms Stronger Than Fear He has covered every major and minor war in Asia from World War II and the Chinese Civil War to the cam paigns in Korea Malaya QuemoyMatsu and Indo nesia Now he writes on Americas biggest hot war of the moment the slow killing struggle going on in Vietnam He has just returned from three months with the troops there and is preparing another evewitness report Vietnam Diary for public ation next fall Following is the first of four exclu sive articles by Tregaskis on the men who today are being shot at and killed to hold the line against Communism EEPRER R e e E Se s S e i s e e co o bSIS B S e e o r F PR W e e F S TN e Se 2 E P g e e ams e S FEESST ESx s a3 e A 5 1 2 et R"
